# macOS / YandexDisk junk
.DS_Store
._*

# Vivado / Vitis build artifacts.
# This repo commits only sources and prebuilt bitstreams; the full projects are
# built elsewhere, so the generated project tree never needs to land here.
*.jou
*.log
*.str
.Xil/
*.cache/
*.hw/
*.runs/
*.gen/
*.sim/
*.ip_user_files/
*.dcp
*.xpr
*.xsa
xsim.dir/
webtalk*.jou
webtalk*.log
usage_statistics_webtalk*
.jobs/

# Intentionally NOT ignored (these are the point of the repo):
#   *.bit / *.bin  — bitstreams and boot images
#   *.uf2          — Pico firmware
#   *.v *.sv *.vhd — HDL sources
#   *.xdc          — constraints
#   *.tcl *.sh     — build/flash scripts
#   *.hex          — memory init / ROM images
